snippet.title: Bloons TD 6 Update 47 Coming Soon | Rogue Legends, New Map, & much more!
snippet.description:
Welcome to a bumper update 47 for Bloons TD 6! Rogue Legends is finally here! Along with an enchanted new map, a magical new skin for Rosalia, and much more! 

Please let us know your feedback in the comments below and happy gaming! :D 

Rogue Legends Video: youtu.be/NerXoyaPCgg
Update notes: http://ninja.kiwi/btd6_47 

Ninja Kiwi Merch Store: https://store.ninjakiwi.com/​
